<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1038015.htm">三星是全球第二大移动端相机制造商</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370638" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/samsung_galaxy_zflip_9411.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/samsung_galaxy_zflip_9411.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/samsung_galaxy_zflip_9411-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/samsung_galaxy_zflip_9411-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/samsung_galaxy_zflip_9411-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>cnBeta 消息，市场调查机构 Strategy Analytics 最新报告指，三星是仅次于索尼的全球第二大移动端相机制造商。2020 年上半年，三星在移动相机传感器市场的营收占比为 32%，索尼的市场份额为 44%，中国图像传感器公司 OmniVision 的收入份额为 9％。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.jiemian.com/article/5084583.html">黄峥：拼多多要在农业领域做重投入和创新</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370639" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wmYPkb8W3o-1dbT_dDassBWbLtxZbgxl9o3oX_aN6F8.jpeg" alt="" width="1200" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wmYPkb8W3o-1dbT_dDassBWbLtxZbgxl9o3oX_aN6F8.jpeg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wmYPkb8W3o-1dbT_dDassBWbLtxZbgxl9o3oX_aN6F8-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wmYPkb8W3o-1dbT_dDassBWbLtxZbgxl9o3oX_aN6F8-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/wmYPkb8W3o-1dbT_dDassBWbLtxZbgxl9o3oX_aN6F8-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>《科创板日报》消息，拼多多董事长黄峥在内部周年庆祝活动上表示，「5 岁的拼多多已经成为一家全社会的公司，肩负着巨大的社会责任」。</p>
<p>黄峥强调，拼多多要在农业领域继续做大量重投入和深度创新。对于未来，黄峥表示拼多多全员都要「开启硬核奋斗模式」。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1038035.htm">Digitimes 预测智能手机出货量实现两位数增长</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370640" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5e68fc4d54f25c381d11733a.jpeg" alt="" width="1136" height="852" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5e68fc4d54f25c381d11733a.jpeg 1136w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5e68fc4d54f25c381d11733a-360x270.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5e68fc4d54f25c381d11733a-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5e68fc4d54f25c381d11733a-1024x768.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1136px) 100vw, 1136px" /></p>
<p>快科技消息，DigiTimes Research 报告指出，在连续三年下降之后，预计 2021 年全球智能手机出货量将实现两位数增长。该报告称，来年的出货量可能增长 1.5 亿部，这主要是由于 5G 在美国，西欧和日本等地区的运营加速。</p>
<p>此外，报告预测三星和苹果在出货量上将分别获全球第一和第二，OPPO、vivo 以及小米则将分别位列 3-5 名。</p>
<h4><a href="https://9to5mac.com/2020/10/08/iphone-for-life/">苹果申请「iPhone for Life」商标</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370641" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone-for-Life-alongside-iPhone-Upgrade-Program.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="512" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone-for-Life-alongside-iPhone-Upgrade-Program.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone-for-Life-alongside-iPhone-Upgrade-Program-360x180.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone-for-Life-alongside-iPhone-Upgrade-Program-768x384.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>9to5mac 消息，苹果于 2020 年 4 月在香港地区申请了「iPhone for Life」商标。报道指，相同商标美国市场虽然没有，但在其它市场曾出现，主要被运营商和苹果门店用于「iPhone Upgrade Program」的项目。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357461" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E8%AF%97%E4%BA%BAlouise-gluck%E8%8E%B7%E5%BE%97%E8%AF%BA%E8%B4%9D%E5%B0%94%E6%96%87%E5%AD%A6%E5%A5%96-11602159921#refreshed">2020 诺贝尔文学奖揭晓</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370642" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/f6c6fb696fef60c2f0a3f9cc5ee9cdcb.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="500" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/f6c6fb696fef60c2f0a3f9cc5ee9cdcb.jpg 500w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/f6c6fb696fef60c2f0a3f9cc5ee9cdcb-360x360.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></p>
<p>《华尔街日报》消息，昨晚，瑞典文学院宣布，将 2020 年诺贝尔文学奖授予美国诗人露易丝・格丽克。获奖理由是，「她清晰无误的诗音、带着朴素的美，使个体存在带有了普遍性。」</p>
<h4><a href="https://cn.nikkei.com/politicsaeconomy/politicsasociety/42277-2020-10-08-10-11-35.html">日本将大幅削减奥运经费</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370643" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/shiyuan.jpg" alt="" width="2048" height="1365" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/shiyuan.jpg 2048w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/shiyuan-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/shiyuan-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/shiyuan-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px" /></p>
<p>《日经中文网》消息，东京奥组委近日提交报告称，将削减奥运 300 亿日元（约人民币 19.2 亿元）成本，举办「简化奥运会」。</p>
<p>9 月，东京奥组委与国际奥委会达成协议，确定了服务水平和调整场馆装饰等简化奥运会的 52 项具体措施。</p>
<h4>阿迪达斯发布 FUTURECRAFT.STRUNG 概念跑鞋</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370644" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/WechatIMG679.jpeg" alt="" width="2000" height="1284" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/WechatIMG679.jpeg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/WechatIMG679-360x231.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/WechatIMG679-768x493.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/WechatIMG679-1024x657.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>阿迪达斯发布 FUTURECRAFT.STRUNG 概念跑鞋，采用了诞生自 FUTURECRAFT 实验室的 STRUNG 鞋面制造技术，搭配新款轻质 ADIDAS 4D 科技中底。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370646" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/WechatIMG675_meitu_1-1.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="667" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/WechatIMG675_meitu_1-1.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/WechatIMG675_meitu_1-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/WechatIMG675_meitu_1-1-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>在数据驱动下，鞋面为一体式无缝设计，重量约为 35 克，全鞋仅重 250 克左右。</p>
<h4><a href="http://news.mtime.com/2020/10/08/1604276.html">艾伦·索金想拍《社交网络 2》，揭露 Facebook 黑暗面</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1370647" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/original-1.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="405" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/original-1.jpg 720w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/original-1-360x203.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></p>
<p>时光网消息，艾伦・索金近日表示，想写《社交网络》续集，但有一个条件，需要大卫・芬奇回归执导。</p>
<p>索金表示，原片制片人斯科特・鲁丁对此也感兴趣。两人连剧本素材都选好了，想改编 2019 年出版的揭露 Facebook 公司黑暗面的《Zucked》一书。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>外国人实名羡慕中国黄金周</h4>
<p>近日来，全国各大旅游景点和车站、机场人头攒动的一幕幕，吸引了世界的目光。外国媒体、专家和网友「实名羡慕」。</p>
<p>网友：「快乐背后我们也付出了很多。」「感谢那些为抗疫付出的所有人。」「舍不得国庆！」</p>